import React from 'react'
import {Route,Switch,Router} from 'react-router-dom'
import Login from './login'
import Card from './Card'

const App1=()=>{
    return(
        <>
        <Router>
            <Switch>
                <Route exact path="/" component={Login} />
                <Route path="/card" component={Card} />
            </Switch>
        </Router>
        </>
    )
}

export default App1;
